{"tid":1371185,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做個好市民，向申訴專員投訴地政總署及發展局","createTime":"2019-07-27T08:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:54:47.000Z","uid":32722,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d890c640c1414c4e1418992b7f325a4c7b10277f","tid":1371185,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:09:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的，大家係政府到做都知高層最怕Omb仔<br />\n中親Omb仔起碼要寫十幾頁薯仔文，仲要俾署長endorse<br />\n既然係咁，咪一於投訴地政總署同發展局唔處理丁屋僭建<br />\n其實唔處理丁屋僭建唔係地政總署同屋宇署既問題<br />\n係發展局對呢件事既政策，所以我地要omb埋發展區<br />\n睇下究竟係地政同屋宇署懶，定係發展局政策<br />\n萬一真係發展局政策，咁大家知點做啦？<br />\n<br />\n又，其實地政總署對一些違規事件可以收取容忍費直至得閒處理/政策出台<br />\n但係地政總署就一直冇咁做，咁係對我地普通既納稅人唔公平，所以要用錢既角度煮重佢地米<br />\n<br />\n希望大家用幾方鐘幫下社會<br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n1. 申訴專員網址：<a href=\"https://www.ombudsman.hk/zh-hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ombudsman.hk%2Fzh-hk%2F&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT10ZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=d74fd26b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ombudsman.hk/zh-hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n2. <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNcJb3X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNcJb3X.png&h=2b4278bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBYPR4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBYPR4b.png&h=862fc258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 投訴者名可以唔係真<br />\n<br />\n5. 地址：總之係一個你可以收到佢寄既信既地址<br />\n<br />\n6. 電話：當然唔填<br />\n<br />\n7. 電郵地址：新開的dummy email戶口<br />\n<br />\n8. <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfO4FYD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfO4FYD.png&h=36d147f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家用幾分鐘迫發展區表態，睇下係咪政府決定漠視丁屋僭建？"},{"pid":"9a096d031f976597c707ba68c4a3e12b75e71926","tid":1371185,"uid":220818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03dac6d476e0c829194790127a37d79923fe8c14","tid":1371185,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:51:5